name: jordan-blake-portfolio
title: Jordan Blake Portfolio
desc: Jordan Blake Portfolio is a sleek, free template built with Astro.js, designed to help developers showcase their projects and skills in a modern, responsive format. Perfect for creating a professional online presence with ease.
article: Jordan Blake Portfolio is a modern, free template crafted for web developers who want to showcase their work in a professional and visually striking manner. Built with Astro.js, this template leverages the power of TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and GSAP to deliver a fast, responsive, and highly customizable experience. Whether you're highlighting your projects, providing contact information, or showcasing your skills, this template offers a polished and efficient solution. Perfect for developers at any stage, Jordan Blake Portfolio makes it easy to create an impressive online presence that reflects your expertise and style.
